// Connections:
/*
 Wiring Connections (Without Resistor)
1️⃣ MQ-2 Gas Sensor (Detects Gas Leakage)
VCC → 5V (Arduino)

GND → GND (Arduino)

A0 → A0 (Arduino)

2️⃣ Buzzer (Alarm)
Positive (+) → D6 (Arduino)

Negative (-) → GND (Arduino)

3️⃣ Servo Motor (Valve Control)
VCC (Red wire) → 5V (Arduino)

GND (Black wire) → GND (Arduino)

Signal (Yellow/White wire) → D9 (Arduino)

4️⃣ IRF540N MOSFET (Fan Control, No Resistor)
Gate (G) → D5 (Arduino) (Direct Connection, No Resistor)

Drain (D) → Negative Terminal of Exhaust Fan

Source (S) → GND (Arduino & Power Supply)

5️⃣ Exhaust Fan (Ventilation)
Positive (+) Terminal → External Power Supply (5V or 12V)

Negative (-) Terminal → MOSFET Drain (D)

6️⃣ Power Connections
Arduino 5V → Sensor & Servo Power

Arduino GND → Sensor, Servo, Fan, and MOSFET Source */
